\mathcal{L}^{ms}_{feat}=\sum^{4}_{l=1}\alpha_{l}\left[MSE\left(\phi_{l}\left(F^{l}_{S}\right),F^{l}_{T}\right)+\beta\cdot\left(1-\cos\left(\phi_{l}\left(F^{l}_{S}\right),F^{l}_{T}\right)\right)\right]
\]

\end_inset

oferă gradienți la fiecare adâncime a rețelei de bază,
